":1,"text":"Lit the glory of that light"},{"kind":"text","text":" I was led by the hand by those who were with me, and went into Damascus. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 9:8","book":"Act","chapter":9,"verse":8,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 16:30","book":"Act","chapter":16,"verse":30,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ac 9:8","book":"Act","chapter":9,"verse":8},{"label":"Ac 16:30","book":"Act","chapter":16,"verse":30}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Lit the glory of that light"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Act:22:12","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Someone named Ananias, a devout man according to the law, who had a good reputation with all the Jews living there, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 9:10","book":"Act","chapter":9,"verse":10,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 9:17","book":"Act","chapter":9,"verse":17,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 10:22","book":"Act","chapter":10,"verse":22,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ac 9:10","book":"Act","chapter":9,"verse":10},{"label":"Ac 9:17","book":"Act","chapter":9,"verse":17},{"label":"Ac 10:22","book":"Act","chapter":10,"verse":22}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Act:22:13","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"came and stood by me and said, ‘Brother Saul, regain your sight.’ And in that very hour I looked up and saw him. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Act:22:14","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"And he said, ‘The God of our ancestors has appointed "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 3:13","book":"Act","chapter":3,"verse":13,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 9:15","book":"Act","chapter":9,"verse":15,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 26:16","book":"Act","chapter":26,"verse":16,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" you to know his will, to see "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 9:1","book":"1Co","chapter":9,"verse":1,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 15:8","book":"1Co","chapter":15,"verse":8,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"text","text":" the Righteous One, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 3:14","book":"Act","chapter":3,"verse":14,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 7:52","book":"Act","chapter":7,"verse":52,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"text","text":" and to hear the words from his mouth, "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ac 3:13","book":"Act","chapter":3,"verse":13},{"label":"Ac 9:15","book":"Act","chapter":9,"verse":15},{"label":"Ac 26:16","book":"Act","chapter":26,"verse":16},{"label":"1Co 9:1","book":"1Co","chapter":9,"verse":1},{"label":"1Co 15:8","book":"1Co","chapter":15,"verse":8},{"label":"Ac 3:14","book":"Act","chapter":3,"verse":14},{"label":"Ac 7:52","book":"Act","chapter":7,"verse":52}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Act:22:15","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"since you will be a witness for him to all people of what you have seen and heard. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 23:11","book":"Act","chapter":23,"verse":11,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 26:16","book":"Act","chapter":26,"verse":16,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ac 23:11","book":"Act","chapter":23,"verse":11},{"label":"Ac 26:16","book":"Act","chapter":26,"verse":16}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Act:22:16","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"And now, why are you delaying? Get up and be baptized, and wash away your sins, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 2:38","book":"Act","chapter":2,"verse":38,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 6:11","book":"1Co","chapter":6,"verse":11,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 10:22","book":"Heb","chapter":10,"verse":22,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" calling on his name.’ "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 9:14","book":"Act","chapter":9,"verse":14,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 10:13","book":"Rom","chapter":10,"verse":13,"letter":"e"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ac 2:38","book":"Act","chapter":2,"verse":38},{"label":"1Co 6:11","book":"1Co","chapter":6,"verse":11},{"label":"Heb 10:22","book":"Heb","chapter":10,"verse":22},{"label":"Ac 9:14","book":"Act","chapter":9,"verse":14},{"label":"Rm 10:13","book":"Rom","chapter":10,"verse":13}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Act:22:17","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“After I returned to Jerusalem and was praying in the temple, I fell into a trance "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 9:26","book":"Act","chapter":9,"verse":26,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 10:10","book":"Act","chapter":10,"verse":10,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ac 9:26","book":"Act","chapter":9,"verse":26},{"label":"Ac 10:10","book":"Act","chapter":10,"verse":10}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Act:22:18","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"and saw him telling me, ‘Hurry and get out of Jerusalem quickly, because they will not accept your testimony about me.’"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Act:22:19","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“But I said, ‘Lord, they know that in synagogue after synagogue I had those who believed in you imprisoned and beaten. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 10:17","book":"Mat","chapter":10,"verse":17,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 8:3","book":"Act","chapter":8,"verse":3,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 22:4","book":"Act","chapter":22,"verse":4,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 10:17","book":"Mat","chapter":10,"verse":17},{"label":"Ac 8:3","book":"Act","chapter":8,"verse":3},{"label":"Ac 22:4","book":"Act","chapter":22,"verse":4}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Act:22:20","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"And when the blood of your witness Stephen was being shed, I stood there giving approval "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Other mss add of his murder"},{"kind":"text","text":" and guarding the clothes of those who killed him.’ "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 7:58","book":"Act","chapter":7,"verse":58,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 8:1","book":"Act","chapter":8,"verse":1,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 1:32","book":"Rom","chapter":1,"verse":32,"letter":"c"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ac 7:58","book":"Act","chapter":7,"verse":58},{"label":"Ac 8:1","book":"Act","chapter":8,"verse":1},{"label":"Rm 1:32","book":"Rom","chapter":1,"verse":32}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Other mss add of his murder"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Act:22:21","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“He said to me, ‘Go, because I will send you far away to the Gentiles.’” "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 9:15","book":"Act","chapter":9,"verse":15,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 13:46","book":"Act","chapter":13,"verse":46,"letter":"b"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ac 9:15","book":"Act","chapter":9,"verse":15},{"label":"Ac 13:46","book":"Act","chapter":13,"verse":46}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Act:22:22","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"They listened to him up to this point. Then they raised their voices, shouting, “Wipe this man off the face of the earth! He should not be allowed to live!” "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 21:36","book":"Act","chapter":21,"verse":36,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 25:24","book":"Act","chapter":25,"verse":24,"letter":"b"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ac 21:36","book":"Act","chapter":21,"verse":36},{"label":"Ac 25:24","book":"Act","chapter":25,"verse":24}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Act:22:23","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"As they were yelling and flinging aside their garments and throwing dust into the air, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Sm 16:13","book":"2Sa","chapter":16,"verse":13,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 7:58","book":"Act","chapter":7,"verse":58,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"2Sm 16:13","book":"2Sa","chapter":16,"verse":13},{"label":"Ac 7:58","book":"Act","chapter":7,"verse":58}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Act:22:24","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"the commander ordered him to be brought into the barracks, directing that he be interrogated with the scourge to discover the reason they were shouting against him like this. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Act:22:25","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"As they stretched him out for the lash, Paul said to the centurion standing by, “Is it legal for you to scourge a man who is a Roman citizen and is uncondemned?” "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 16:37","book":"Act","chapter":16,"verse":37,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 21:34","book":"Act","chapter":21,"verse":34,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 22:29","book":"Act","chapter":22,"verse":29,"letter":"c"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ac 16:37","book":"Act","chapter":16,"verse":37},{"label":"Ac 21:34","book":"Act","chapter":21,"verse":34},{"label":"Ac 22:29","book":"Act","chapter":22,"verse":29}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Act:22:26","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"When the centurion heard this, he went and reported to the commander, saying, “What are you going to do? For this man is a Roman citizen.”"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Act:22:27","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The commander came and said to him, “Tell me, are you a Roman citizen?”"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Act:22:28","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The commander replied, “I bought this citizenship for a large amount of money.”"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Act:22:29","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"So those who were about to examine him withdrew from him immediately. The commander too was alarmed when he realized Paul was a Roman citizen and he had bound him. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 16:38","book":"Act","chapter":16,"verse":38,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 21:33","book":"Act","chapter":21,"verse":33,"letter":"b"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ac 16:38","book":"Act","chapter":16,"verse":38},{"label":"Ac 21:33","book":"Act","chapter":21,"verse":33}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Act:22:30","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The next day, since he wanted to find out exactly why Paul was being accused by the Jews, he released him "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Other mss add from his chains"},{"kind":"text","text":" and instructed the chief priests and all the Sanhedrin to convene. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 5:22","book":"Mat","chapter":5,"verse":22,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 23:3–8","book":"Act","chapter":23,"verse":3,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" He brought Paul down and placed him before them."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 5:22","book":"Mat","chapter":5,"verse":22},{"label":"Ac 23:3–8","book":"Act","chapter":23,"verse":3}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Other mss add from his chains"}]}]},"cachedAt":1783099529156}